Josh Hirsberg



Mr. Josh Hirsberg is Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & VP at Marina District Finance Co., Inc. and Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & Executive VP at Boyd Gaming Corp. Mr. Hirsberg was previously employed as Chief Financial & Accounting Officer by Marina District Development Co. LLC, Treasurer & Vice President by Caesars Entertainment, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by Edge Star Partners LLC, and VP-Strategic Planning & Investor Relations by Harrah's Entertainment, Inc.



