Josh Hirsberg











































Home » Josh Hirsberg
Enterprise OperationsPeople/Property
Josh Hirsberg


February 28, 2008



        Reprints
      






        No Comments
      



Josh Hirsberg has joined Las Vegas-based Boyd Gaming as senior  vice president and chief financial offer. A 17 year veteran of the  gaming industry, Hirsberg most recently served as chief financial  officer for EdgeStar Partners, as Las Vegas-based resort development  company. He previously held several senior-level finance positions in  the gaming industry, including vice president and treasurer for Caesars  Entertainment and vice president of strategic planning and investor  relations for Harrah’s Entertainment.





